features: MFi Certification: earbuds wired, works with all devices with Lightning connector and supports all versions of iOS, perfectly compatible with iPhone 14/14Plus/14Pro/14 Pro Max/13/13 Mini/13 Pro/13 Pro Max/12/12 Mini/12 Pro/12 Pro Max/11/11 Pro/11 Pro Max/X/XS/XS Max/XR/8/8P/7/7P.

Microphone & Volume Control: The headphone cable comes with a built-in microphone and controller. A single multifunctional button allows you to answer/end a call, play/pause, jump and play songs with the headphones. No need to take out your phone. Built-in microphone allows you to call hands free.
High-quality sound: iPhone wired earphones provide outstanding sound quality, delivering clear, balanced, and deep audio, making listening to music, watching movies, or making calls more enjoyable.

Ergonomic Design: The in-ear diameter of the iphone wired earphones is only 6mm, which avoids squeezing and stuffy feeling and keeps stable. Ecoamica has scanned the ear canal data of thousands of people and applied good ergonomics. Two pairs of included eartips enhance the seal and block out external noise, allowing you to enjoy music on your iOS device with these comfortable in-ear wired headphones.

What You Get: 2* Earbuds headphones wired compatible with the latest iPhone devices, three-button control, easy to talk and skip songs, and it could be a pleasant gift to a friend.If you have any questions, please do not hesitate to contact us.Our service team will reply you with satisfied solution within 24 hours.
